
Use sheet border in your cellview:

A new system library called "sheetBorder" is added to our system library
set.  It is used by Cadence's software for sheet border.

The old US_8th sheet border is for backward compatibility only, it will
not be used in the future.

To add sheet border to your current schematic in Composer, you may
use the Sheet->Edit Size menu item to add a specific sheet border
size and type to your schematic.

You can always changed the size later by Sheet->Edit Size menu item.

The title block can be edit using Sheet->Edit Title command.

More information can be obtained from the Cadence Virtuoso Schematic
Editor User's Guide.
